readable.content: A brown and a black and brown dog are playing in the water and the black one is carrying a long stick in its mouth . A dog runs through the water with a stick while another dog stands there . Two dogs are running through a wet , grassy area and one is carrying a long stick . Two dogs fight over a stick in a flooded field . Two dogs playing in a flooded field with a stick .
